					"type": 23,
					"value": "In the Bhaal Temple, Orin may kill the abductee during dialog due to a failed Skillcheck or players encouraging her to kill them.\r\n\r\nThis is the PAD that plays reacting to the dead abductee after the battle.\r\n\r\nThe abductee could be Laezel, Minthara, Gale, Halsin or Yenna."
